{"meta":{"title":"Moroni 4","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/4?lang=spa","contentType":"text/html","audio":[{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ/2017-11-2330-moroni-04-64k-spa.mp3?download=true","voice":{"name":"audio"}}],"pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"5784db1d92698e5430d1d6af7629fff2589d344d","data-aid":"124251156","data-aid-version":"4","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/4","itemscope":"","itemtype":"http://schema.org/Article","lang":"spa","data-orig-id":"3e1ae322e4eeed3898d379132f1dd2011137ebbd","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"Moroni 4","description":"Se expone la forma en que los élderes y los presbíteros administran el pan sacramental. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C."},"pageSocial":{"title":"Moroni 4","description":"Se expone la forma en que los élderes y los presbíteros administran el pan sacramental. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"124251255\" id=\"title_number1\">Capítulo 4</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"124251256\" id=\"study_summary1\">Se expone la forma en que los élderes y los presbíteros administran el pan sacramental. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124251257\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>La <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>forma</a> en que sus <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>élderes</a> y presbíteros administraban la carne y la sangre de Cristo a la iglesia; y las <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>administraban</a> de acuerdo con los mandamientos de Cristo; por tanto, sabemos que la manera es correcta; y el élder o el presbítero las administraba.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124251258\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>Y se arrodillaban con la iglesia, y oraban al Padre en el nombre de Cristo, diciendo:</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124251259\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>Oh Dios, Padre Eterno, en el nombre de Jesucristo, tu Hijo, te pedimos que bendigas y santifiques este <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>pan</a> para las almas de todos los que participen de él, para que lo coman en <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>memoria</a> del cuerpo de tu Hijo, y testifiquen ante ti, oh Dios, Padre Eterno, que están dispuestos a tomar sobre sí el <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>nombre</a> de tu Hijo, y a recordarle siempre, y a guardar sus mandamientos que él les ha dado, para que siempre puedan tener su <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3d\"><sup class=\"marker\">d</sup>Espíritu</a> consigo. Amén.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"4\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124251260\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.1-7?lang=spa#p1\">3 Ne. 18:1–7</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note1b\" data-full-marker=\"1b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124251262\" id=\"note1b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/elder?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Élder (anciano)</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note1c\" data-full-marker=\"1c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124251263\" id=\"note1c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.76-77?lang=spa#p76\">DyC 20:76–77</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note3a\" data-full-marker=\"3a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124251265\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/sacrament?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Santa Cena</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note3b\" data-full-marker=\"3b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124251266\" id=\"note3b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/luke/22.19?lang=spa#p19\">Lucas 22:19</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/1-cor/11.23-24?lang=spa#p23\">1 Cor. 11:23–24</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.7?lang=spa#p7\">3 Ne. 18:7</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note3c\" data-full-marker=\"3c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124251267\" id=\"note3c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/jesus-christ?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Jesucristo — El tomar sobre sí el nombre de Jesucristo</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"d\" id=\"note3d\" data-full-marker=\"3d\">\n<p data-aid=\"124251268\" id=\"note3d_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/holy-ghost?lang=spa\"><small>GEE</small> Espíritu Santo</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","associated":{"title_number1":[{"sizes":"250px","alt":"La bendición de la Santa Cena","aspectRatio":"0.6666666666666666","height":"480","width":"320","missingAsset":"false","assetId":"4032b9ebee7fc0b2e3dceb8d519ed720f47b5e06","srcset":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/d0/d9/d0d9d491433fd36c464db2234b33da3478b2f549/deacons_sacrament_paraguay.jpeg 60w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/cd/ec/cdec282a86aa0b605707dd8b33b49600d821e2b0/deacons_sacrament_paraguay.jpeg 100w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/fc/08/fc083c35b6d44a5496a3430fcc9ff19a9f9f5524/deacons_sacrament_paraguay.jpeg 200w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/eb/4a/eb4a797a541105b3afccacd362682bd817d37ca3/deacons_sacrament_paraguay.jpeg 250w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/